// 撜啣嘶 + ???????其葉?隤?
peakLockTxt = peakFloorOn ? "?????? + (effBreathGB ? " 瘜Ｗ??" + str.tostring(breathMult, "#.0") : "") + (effStallRatchet and stallShrink < 0.999 ? " 撟湧翩?嗥??" + str.tostring(stallShrink, "#.0") : "") : "??????
