modLine7  = usePureA ? "?? : ("??瘜Ｗ??芷??頝?F1):" + (effAddSpaceVol?"??:"??) + " ??蟡冽銵圈?駁◢??F2):" + (effVoteFade?"??:"??) + (effVoteFade ? "(?? + str.tostring(voteFadeCuts) + ")" : ""))
